{"type":"message","id":"448be597","parentId":"05e2948f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T00:15:55.670Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-12 19:00:58 GMT-5] WhatsApp gateway connected.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/Gustavo/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Sunday, April 12th, 2026 — 7:15 PM (America/Bogota) / 2026-04-13 00:15 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776039355669}}
